      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 134,
      "message": "InputStream deals with IO, hence - you cannot know if it is empty by checking if it is null (null would only suggest that you initialised the IO stream object in a valid way).\nIn order to check wether there's data coming, I would suggest using the available() method.",
