      "message": "Concept of this yaml parser was to introduce stream-base mechanism for parsing yaml, so proper flow would be to parse a content -> apply all the filters -> consume the results (At this level streams which stores the content are already closed). \n\nAlso if You will check next merge requests about GAB - the usage of GABYamlParser is planned such way to provide data and filters and make single call for the response. I mean that this parser is rather to handle single requests for filtering the file content not to making a complicated transformations of the data.",
